    "description": [
      "A thin westward trail has been worn out of the dense boreal woodland.  Spruce and pine boughs bend low over the path as if resentful of its intrusion into their domain.  The trees are heavy-laden with white snow, the undersides of many branches sharp with icicles that gleam in the aurora's light.  A silvery river flows sluggishly past the trees clustered to the south of the pathway."
